Package: rustyfoot-hmi
Version: 1.0.0
Architecture: arm64
Maintainer: Dataforte <info@dataforte.fi>
Description: Rustyfoot HMI for MOD Audio
 Flutter-based touchscreen interface for MOD Audio's mod-ui system,
 designed for Raspberry Pi.
Depends: rustyfoot, libdrm2, libgbm1, libsystemd0, libinput10, libxkbcommon0, libudev1, libegl1, libgles2, libvulkan1, libgstreamer1.0-0, libgstreamer-plugins-base1.0-0, libglib2.0-0, libatomic1, fonts-freefont-ttf
